#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:2
msgid "PowerShell"
msgstr "PowerShell"

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:5
msgid "执行策略"
msgstr "Execution Policy"

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:6
msgid ""
"PowerShell 提供了 "
"Restricted、AllSigned、RemoteSigned、Unrestricted、Bypass、Undefined "
"六种类型的执行策略。"
msgstr ""
"PowerShell provides six execution policy types: Restricted, AllSigned, "
"RemoteSigned, Unrestricted, Bypass, and Undefined."

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:8
msgid "Restricted 策略可以执行单个的命令，但是不能执行脚本，Windows 8、 Windows Server 2012中默认使用该策略。"
msgstr "The Restricted policy can execute individual commands but cannot run scripts. Windows 8 and Windows Server 2012 use this policy by default."

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:10
msgid "AllSigned 策略允许执行所有具有数字签名的脚本。"
msgstr "The AllSigned policy allows all scripts with digital signatures to run."

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:12
msgid ""
"RemoteSigned "
"当执行从网络上下载的脚本时，需要脚本具有数字签名，否则不会运行这个脚本。如果是在本地创建的脚本则可以直接执行，不要求脚本具有数字签名。"
msgstr ""
"Under RemoteSigned, scripts downloaded from the internet must have a digital "
"signature; otherwise, they will not run. Locally created scripts can run "
"directly without a digital signature."

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:14
msgid "Unrestricted 这是一种比较宽容的策略，允许运行未签名的脚本。对于从网络上下载的脚本，在运行前会进行安全性提示。"
msgstr "Unrestricted is a more permissive policy that allows unsigned scripts to run. Scripts downloaded from the internet trigger a security prompt before execution."

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:16
msgid "BypassBypass 执行策略对脚本的执行不设任何的限制，任何脚本都可以执行，并且不会有安全性提示。"
msgstr "The Bypass execution policy places no restrictions on script execution. Any script can run, and no security prompt is shown."

#: ../../source/language/powershell.rst:18
msgid "UndefinedUndefined 表示没有设置脚本策略，会继承或使用默认的脚本策略。"
msgstr "Undefined means no script policy is set, so PowerShell inherits or uses the default script policy."

